The '''''Starlight Red''''', formerly known as '''''Faceted''''', was a [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighter]] owned by the [[free-trader]] and [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] known as [[Celia Durasha]] and piloted by her and [[U-THR]]. Before Durasha acquired the ship, it belonged to the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Thune (bounty hunter)|Thune]].

